msgid "Build and run Asterinas"
msgstr "建置並執行 Asterinas"

#: src/kernel/intel-tdx.md:60
msgid "Download the latest source code."
msgstr "下載最新的來源碼。"

#: src/kernel/intel-tdx.md:66
msgid "Run a Docker container as the development environment."
msgstr "執行 Docker 容器作為開發環境。"

