#: src/kernel/linux-compatibility/index.md:1
msgid "Linux Compatibility"
msgstr "Linux 相容性"

#: src/kernel/linux-compatibility/index.md:3
msgid "\"We don't break user space.\""
msgstr ""

#: src/kernel/linux-compatibility/index.md:5
msgid "\\--- Linus Torvalds"
msgstr ""

#: src/kernel/linux-compatibility/index.md:7
msgid ""
"Asterinas is dedicated to maintaining compatibility with the Linux ABI, "
"ensuring that applications and administrative tools designed for Linux can "
"seamlessly operate within Asterinas. While we prioritize compatibility, it "
"is important to note that Asterinas does not, nor will it in the future, "
"support the loading of Linux kernel modules."
msgstr ""
"Asterinas 致力於保持與 Linux ABI 的相容性，確保專為 Linux 設計的應用程式和管"
"理工具能在 Asterinas 中無縫運行。雖然我們優先考慮相容性，但必須注意的是，"
"Asterinas 目前不支援、未來也不會支援載入 Linux 內核模組。"

