msgid "Launch an x86-64 Ubuntu container:"
msgstr "啟動 x86-64 的 Ubuntu 容器："

#: src/distro/index.md:35
msgid "Inside the container, install QEMU:"
msgstr "在容器內安裝 QEMU："

#: src/distro/index.md:42
msgid ""
"Download the latest Asterinas NixOS installer ISO from [GitHub Releases]"
