#: src/osdk/guide/index.md:5
msgid ""
"The Asterinas OSDK (short for Operating System Development Kit) is designed "
"to simplify the development of Rust operating systems. It aims to streamline "
"the process by leveraging [the framekernel architecture](../../kernel/the-"
"framekernel-architecture.md)."
msgstr ""

#: src/osdk/guide/index.md:10
