"The OSDK provides a command-line tool `cargo-osdk`, which facilitates "
"project management for those developed on the framekernel architecture. "
"`cargo-osdk` can be used as a subcommand of Cargo. Much like Cargo for Rust "
"projects, `cargo-osdk` enables building, running, and testing projects "
"conveniently."
msgstr ""
"OSDK 提供了一個命令行工具 `cargo-osdk` ，有助於基於框內核架構開發的專案管理。"
"` cargo-osdk` 可以作為 Cargo 的子命令使用。就像 Cargo 之於 Rust 專案一樣， "
"`cargo-osdk` 讓建置、執行和測試專案變得非常方便。"

