#: src/osdk/guide/intel-tdx.md:3
msgid ""
"The OSDK supports running your OS in an [Intel TDX](https://www.intel.com/"
"content/www/us/en/developer/tools/trust-domain-extensions/overview.html) "
"environment conveniently. Intel TDX can provide a more secure environment "
