msgstr ""

#: src/to-contribute/coding-guidelines/rust-guidelines/select-topics/logging.md:33
msgid "`error!`"
msgstr ""

#: src/to-contribute/coding-guidelines/rust-guidelines/select-topics/logging.md:33
msgid ""
"Serious failures: resource exhaustion, invariant violations caught at "
"runtime."
msgstr ""

#: src/to-contribute/coding-guidelines/rust-guidelines/select-topics/logging.md:35
msgid ""
"A log statement that fires on every syscall or every timer tick must use "
"`trace!`, not `debug!`."
